{"tid":1528980,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"機場逃亡之旅","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:53:54.000Z","uid":235801,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e50d0be4ef6d576a41bda82abca7b44bca9cf4","tid":1528980,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:45:27.000Z","msg":"屌，cls攰到仆街，由機場行到東涌再去到青馬廣場，我都唔知嗰度行咗幾多K，成程都勁撚驚險，中途成日要凝住會有狗車突然間停低捉人，跟住我求其上咗架出巿區嘅巴士。<br />\n<br />\n仆你個臭街，原本係搭去美孚再搭西鐵翻去，當我搭到錦上路，仆你個街原來仲未完，跟住我就收到風屯門元朗天水圍都有狗，嚇都我搭對頭車返美孚再轉巴士先翻到屋企。<br />\n<br />\n想講嘅係就算今次幾咁驚險，我下次都係唔會因為驚而唔出嚟，期待你班黑警比人清算嘅一日。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"973a586ed567b515ef1a0c471f79530353c646ef","tid":1528980,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965b25a52b268534ae7f7d6842709d9411e3b4c6","tid":1528980,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"926bd3006515d87f501bfcfeeea13d3d2e014f20","tid":1528980,"uid":235801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:47:36.000Z","msg":"好撚攰"},{"pid":"771bbe1080d61104ba2c748e981f1e5fb1b1b24f","tid":1528980,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"ching 好好休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae18ce1f06200c1c22bfb9267547b9fdb9182ba","tid":1528980,"uid":147349,"lik